reviews.text: This is the only restaurant that serves seafood Hakka 客家 style, everything from fresh squid吊桶, fresh sea fish 煎马友to poultry is extremely fresh n tasty. My A list definitely for Chinese restaurant.

Very good food with exquisitely selected ingredients. Indigenous Hakka cuisine. But pricewise it is quite costly and seating is a bit tight. HK local style anyway. Worth going for special occasions with friends who treasure great food but do not mind crowded tables.
I used to like this restaurant and it is one of my favourite Hakka restaurants in HK. But I bought half chicken today to take home and it just does not taste right.
Food was nice but very overpriced and dishes were small.
Perfect vietnamese food.

reviews.text:
地點不在大街, 但有品質的食店顧客始終識搵嘢食
吃了一個簡單的午餐, 四季豆回鍋肉, 賣相很簡單, 可以說是普通, 但非常美味, 凍檸檬茶有茶味, 少甜甜度剛好
下次要來試晚市, 有很多小菜, 要來試試
裝修後環境更理想，菜式多款好吃，服務一流
This is the only restaurant that serves seafood Hakka 客家 style, everything from fresh squid吊桶, fresh sea fish 煎马友to poultry is extremely fresh n tasty. My A list definitely for Chinese restaurant.
很傳統的客家菜，最值得一試的是腐魚炒蓮藕苗和黑糖蔗糖黑糖蔗糖蜂巢雪糕非常好味

Very good food with exquisitely selected ingredients. Indigenous Hakka cuisine. But pricewise it is quite costly and seating is a bit tight. HK local style anyway. Worth going for special occasions with friends who treasure great food but do not mind crowded tables.
